                     <interp inst="t16810413-9-person31" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             giving Evidence against him, after the Jury were satisfied of the Statute, they brought him in <rs id="t16810413-9-verdict35" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16810413-9-verdict35" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               guilty
            </rs>; and he was Sentenced to be <rs id="t16810413-9-punish36" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16810413-9-punish36" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
